        to the wrong thread,

10:38.012 --> 10:39.138
so it was pretty awkward.

10:39.180 --> 10:42.975
-Sorry.
        -It's not your fault.

10:43.017 --> 10:45.603
-You look beautiful.
              -Thanks.

10:45.645 --> 10:48.314
And congrats on the GIF.
