11:47.039 --> 11:48.457
You know, if you ever
        find yourself looking

11:48.499 --> 11:51.419
across the room at my son,
     and you don't feel that...

11:52.670 --> 11:55.047
You got
      my blessing to walk away.

11:57.925 --> 12:00.636
