12:32.960 --> 12:35.379
Well, just make sure they
     give you what you're worth.

12:35.421 --> 12:38.257
There isn't enough money
       in the world for that.

12:38.299 --> 12:40.676
That's what my mom said right
     before she divorced my dad.

12:46.932 --> 12:48.184
Ooh.

12:48.225 --> 12:50.269
Hattie, what do you do

12:50.311 --> 12:51.937
when you don't know
   where you stand with your boo?

12:51.979 --> 12:54.106
Well, that's usually
      most of the time for me.

12:54.148 --> 12:57.526
