          with you and Ben?

13:04.325 --> 13:06.076
-Sister to sister?
               -Sure.

13:06.118 --> 13:08.120
Ben's been acting
        really weird lately.

13:08.162 --> 13:09.872
He's a weird guy.

13:09.914 --> 13:10.956
Yeah, but now it's like
        he doesn't even want

13:10.998 --> 13:12.458
to be seen with me.

13:12.500 --> 13:15.127
And I think it's
         because I'm white.

13:15.169 --> 13:17.630
-You're probably right.
    -Yeah, but I can't help that.

13:17.671 --> 13:19.965
And he knew I was white
     when he started dating me.

13:20.007 --> 13:23.344
That's true, but, you know,
         times have changed.

13:23.385 --> 13:25.763
It can't be easy walking around
    with a white boo these days.

13:25.805 --> 13:26.764
If he's not gonna
              accept me

13:26.806 --> 13:28.808
for who I am, what can I do?

13:28.849 --> 13:30.476
Leave his ass.

13:30.518 --> 13:31.811
Or just stick around
          until I implode.

13:34.104 --> 13:36.190
Either way,
         it's gonna be bad.

13:36.232 --> 13:37.817
Normally, I would run this
           by my roommate,

13:37.858 --> 13:39.068
but she moved out
          eight months ago

13:39.109 --> 13:40.569
and blocked me on all socials.

13:40.611 --> 13:43.113
But I still keep up with
    what she's streaming, though.

13:43.155 --> 13:44.990
She still uses my account.

13:45.032 --> 13:46.492
So you still got
           an extra room?

13:46.534 --> 13:47.493
Oh, yeah,
        with a full-size bed

13:47.535 --> 13:48.494
and a record player.

13:48.536 --> 13:50.162
-Full size?
              -Mm-hmm.

13:50.204 --> 13:52.164
Look, let me get your number
   just in case Nia kicks me out.

13:52.206 --> 13:53.999
I might need a backup plan.

13:54.041 --> 13:56.168
-Roomies?
             -Calm down.

13:58.712 --> 14:00.172
Ladies and gentlemen,

14:00.214 --> 14:02.132
welcome to the celebration

14:02.174 --> 14:04.093
of Chuck and Marie's
             engagement.

14:07.179 --> 14:09.598
Son, Marie, as you know,

14:09.640 --> 14:11.350
we've been married
         for over 20 years.

14:11.392 --> 14:13.435
People ask us for advice.

14:13.477 --> 14:14.478
They think we have
        some kind of secret.

14:14.520 --> 14:16.689
And we do.

14:16.730 --> 14:18.190
Don't get divorced.

14:19.900 --> 14:21.485
That's pretty much it.

14:21.527 --> 14:23.153
Good luck, kids.

14:31.078 --> 14:32.246
Okay, I gotta go.

14:32.288 --> 14:33.831
-I gotta go live real quick.
                -Mm!

14:33.873 --> 14:35.416
Yeah, and I gotta go
         holla at somebody.

14:35.457 --> 14:36.584
Who?

14:36.625 --> 14:37.960
Mind the business
           that pays you.

14:38.002 --> 14:39.295
I wanted to say
         goodbye to Chance,

14:39.336 --> 14:41.046
but I can't seem
        to find him anywhere.

14:41.088 --> 14:42.506
I will give him your love.

14:43.966 --> 14:44.925
Bye.

14:46.927 --> 14:48.971
So how you feeling?

14:49.013 --> 14:50.681
Nervous.

14:50.723 --> 14:53.309
-I hear that's normal.
        -Yeah. Yeah, me too.

14:53.350 --> 14:55.519
Well, if you ever
          get too nervous,

14:55.561 --> 14:57.313
just know I'm always here
              for you.

14:57.354 --> 15:00.065
