15:35.643 --> 15:36.769
All right.

15:38.520 --> 15:39.813
Ow!

15:39.855 --> 15:41.941
See, I'm done playing with you.
              I'm good.

15:41.982 --> 15:43.442
What's wrong?

15:43.484 --> 15:44.985
I'm just annoyed.

15:45.027 --> 15:46.528
About what?

15:46.570 --> 15:48.906
This shitty-ass job
      I've being trying to get.

15:48.948 --> 15:53.077
These training days
    are taking up all of my time.

15:53.118 --> 15:55.829
I've been trying to finish
      my rewrite for weeks now.

15:55.871 --> 15:58.207
You gotta be better
      about managing your time.

15:58.248 --> 16:00.459
Yeah, well, I ain't never
   really been good at that, so...

16:00.501 --> 16:01.919
No one is.

16:01.961 --> 16:03.712
That's why
       you have to work at it.

16:03.754 --> 16:05.589
Hmm.

16:05.631 --> 16:06.924
Don't give up on something
            just because

16:06.966 --> 16:09.760
you're not good
          at it right away.

16:09.802 --> 16:11.220
Well, I'm about to give up
        on this old-ass game

16:11.261 --> 16:12.721
that you're trying to make--

16:12.763 --> 16:15.641
You wouldn't say that
      if your ass was winning.

16:15.683 --> 16:17.309
Can we go bowling next time?

16:17.351 --> 16:19.311
Bowling is so unsanitary.

16:19.353 --> 16:21.146
Germs are good for you!

16:21.188 --> 16:22.648
You know I'm a germaphobe.

16:22.690 --> 16:26.068
No wonder why your bathroom
      is always squeaky clean.

16:26.110 --> 16:29.154
I was like, "She like the Black
    Mommie Dearest or something."

16:29.196 --> 16:30.572
I'm also a neat freak.

16:30.614 --> 16:32.366
Oh, you definitely a freak.

16:32.408 --> 16:35.077
Every time
          I close my eyes--

16:35.119 --> 16:36.537
Uh-uh, don't make me
          come over there.

16:36.578 --> 16:38.664
I want you to, come on!

16:38.706 --> 16:41.417
I wake up
           feeling so horny

16:41.458 --> 16:42.918
-What you do about that?
            -Oh, I know.

16:42.960 --> 16:45.921
I can't get you
            out of my mind

16:45.963 --> 16:49.425
- Sexing you is all I see
              -Come on!

16:49.466 --> 16:53.095
I would give anything

16:53.137 --> 16:55.806
Just to make you
            understand me

16:55.848 --> 16:57.683
Ey!

16:57.725 --> 17:00.436
I don't give a damn
          about nothing else

17:00.477 --> 17:02.896
Freaking you is all...

17:02.938 --> 17:05.315
Today was really nice.

17:05.357 --> 17:07.151
Yeah.

17:07.192 --> 17:09.194
It's good having everybody
