17:11.321 --> 17:13.490
Thank you
    for including me in all this.

17:13.532 --> 17:15.284
Of course.

17:15.325 --> 17:16.952
Wouldn't have it any other way.

17:19.913 --> 17:20.914
Are you scared?

17:23.167 --> 17:24.877
Of what?

17:24.918 --> 17:26.962
Becoming that dude.

17:27.004 --> 17:28.547
What dude?

17:28.589 --> 17:30.841
The perfect Black dude,

17:30.883 --> 17:33.385
with the beautiful wife
