          to be that dude.

17:40.517 --> 17:42.227
I know you have.

17:46.899 --> 17:50.569
What about you?
      You ready to be that guy?

17:50.611 --> 17:52.237
I don't know.

17:54.239 --> 17:56.158
I'm sure Nia's at home
             tacking you

17:56.200 --> 17:57.743
on her vision board right now.

17:57.785 --> 17:59.912
I'm sure.

18:02.122 --> 18:04.583
What are you gonna do?

18:04.625 --> 18:07.669
Just be single and handsome
      for the rest of your life

18:07.711 --> 18:08.837
and keep posting pictures
               of you

18:08.879 --> 18:10.214
and your abs on vacation?

18:10.255 --> 18:12.049
Hey, that got me
         an endorsement deal

18:12.091 --> 18:13.884
with a travel agency.
             Don't hate.

18:21.975 --> 18:24.186
