         another guy since?

19:47.644 --> 19:50.355
Nope.

19:50.397 --> 19:52.191
Well, I feel special.

19:57.029 --> 20:00.365
Do you ever think about it?

20:00.407 --> 20:03.660
soft R&B music playing

20:03.702 --> 20:05.579
