20:05.621 --> 20:08.415
About what our lives
           could have been

20:08.457 --> 20:10.876
if we didn't have
       so much to live up to?

20:18.425 --> 20:21.345
I think about it
            all the time.

20:21.386 --> 20:23.180
Me too.

20:23.222 --> 20:24.514
But I definitely
         still feel the need

20:24.556 --> 20:26.308
to be a good Black son.

20:26.350 --> 20:29.019
