21:23.991 --> 21:25.200
Why?

21:28.662 --> 21:30.622
'Cause I don't want
            to lose her.

21:48.849 --> 21:51.768
heartfelt music playing

22:05.449 --> 22:08.452
I stumble sometimes

22:12.706 --> 22:16.043
I lay awake at night

22:20.088 --> 22:23.550
I drink and I cry

22:25.719 --> 22:27.346
Marie?

22:27.387 --> 22:29.181
'Cause I'm only strong
